{"tid":369057,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"律政司是否有政治動機？石永泰：「50/50。信則有、不信則無」","createTime":"2017-08-22T04:19:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T05:54:43.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"be41f0a422f1c832cca16963aaa030e7f77984ff","tid":369057,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T04:19:40.000Z","msg":"石永泰在節目表示，自己只是講出「hard fact（殘酷現實），講出大家都唔願講嘅真相」。至於律政司是否有政治動機，他形容是「50、50。信則有、不信則無」，只有從客觀事實看再推論，但不幸的是，今次案件涉及黃之鋒等三名較「high-profile（高調）」的人。<br />\n<br />\n石永泰指出，明白很多人有憂慮，惟「好難為了呃LIKE走去話一定有政治動機」。他解釋，法例容許覆核，兩方也可以覆核刑期，「法律畀呢個權，人人平等」，無理由因有抗爭者牽涉在內，檢控一方便不進行「法律」或「政策」理由上的覆核。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，「如果一個政治人，參與公民抗命，除非佢（檢控）係屈你殺人放火強姦，完全風馬牛不相及罪行，但如果係告你當日相關罪行，拋個身出來灑熱血，carry on你嘅志願，唔好喺度計較或者咩，或者同行嗌一啲稍為唔理智口號」，直言有些口號已超越理性。<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170822/s00001/1503363249902\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170822%2Fs00001%2F1503363249902&d=wlJq7LVdHrOkDtjVdIz6VIS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=16f5cad0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170822%2Fs00001%2F1503363249902&h=800fb0de\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170822/s00001/1503363249902</a>"},{"pid":"de23cf62732694afaf0749c3a2938347ac161180","tid":369057,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T04:29:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">12碼...！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"718e0bef3c799a18754c566e29fb53258eead961","tid":369057,"uid":44358,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T04:34:25.000Z","msg":"佢都戇尻既，問題係刑罰根本唔合理。<br />\n<br />\n講來講去，乜野求仁得仁，咁劉曉波被以言入罪，又算唔算求仁得仁<img src=\"/assets/fa